MarkupText: DTWUMI [62]: For each gap, this approach finds the most similar window to the subsequence after (resp. before) the gap based on the combination of shape- features extraction and Dynamic Time Warping algo- rithms. Then, the previous (resp. following) window of the most similar one in the incomplete signal is used to complete the gap.
